name: ACQUA DI GIÒ
description: Acqua di Giò is a tempting, fresh aquatic fragrance which explores another side of pleasure. A thirst for foreign lands, a certain taste for escape, a scent which is fresh yet full of passion. The essence of Acqua is an exploration of its source – an extra-sensory adventure, travelling with the flow wherever it may lead. And its essence is in the air!
